text: Iván Fandiño Barros (September 29, 1980 – June 17, 2017) was an award winningAward winning matador Ivan Fandino dies after being fatally gored in bullfight Spanish bullfighter. He was born in Orduña-Urduña, Spain. Fandiño died of injuries he sustained after being gored by a bull on June 17, 2017 in Aire-sur-l'Adour, France, aged 36.Spanish matador dies after being gored during bullfight ==References== ==Other websites== Category:1980 births Category:2017 deaths Category:Deaths in sport Category:Spanish sportspeople
